<doc id="1184645" wikidata="Q7431773" url="?curid=1184645" title="Schmaltz herring">
<text>Schmaltz herring is herring caught just before spawning, when the fat (&quot;schmaltz&quot; in Yiddish) in the fish is at a maximum. Colloquially, &quot;schmaltz herring&quot; refers to this fish pickled in brine: see pickled herring.

