=== Confluence Music Festival ===
The Confluence Music Festival is an annual multi-day event during the NASCAR Cup Series race weekend, featuring both acclaimed and local artists. 
===Other events===
During the winter months after the racing season concludes, World Wide Technology Raceway&#x27;s oval track infield transforms into the WonderLight&#x27;s drive-through Christmas light display.

